com.yashovardhan99.timeit

Interface Stopwatch.OnTickListener

  • Enclosing class:
    Stopwatch

    public static interface Stopwatch.OnTickListener
    Interface to listen for stopwatch tick events every time clock is updated. Useful for scenarios where you want to do more than update a textField based on time. Created by Yashovardhan99 on 10/12/18 as a part of TimeIt.
    Since:
    1.2
    Author:
    Yashovardhan Dhanania

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onTick(Stopwatch stopwatch)
      Called every time the clock 'ticks'.

    • Method Detail

      • onTick

        void onTick(Stopwatch stopwatch)
        Called every time the clock 'ticks'. The stopwatch ticks after a delay of 100ms (or as specified).
        Parameters:
        stopwatch - Reference to the currently calling stopwatch.
        Since:
        1.2
